description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation - Blissful Deep Relaxation' from the channel The Honest Guys - Meditations - Relaxation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This guided meditation will gently ease you into a state of blissfully deep relaxation. Join our community/see our products: https://www.thehonestguys.co.uk/products

We create effortless ways for anyone to reach a profound sense of deep relaxation, meditation and sleep, without ever having to try. We offer this through high-quality audio productions, called 'guided visualisations'. These include sleep talk-downs, meditations, wonderful fantasy imagery and stories.
